 A few days ago,

277
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:18,260
 I saw the future of a girl who was just passing by.

278
00:20:18,260 --> 00:20:21,080
 That day when Yun Gi came,

279
00:20:21,080 --> 00:20:23,920
 I saw his memories.

280
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:28,030
 Did you perhaps  do something to me?

