00:24:20,300 --> 00:24:25,570
Your appearing in front of me that day was also a miracle for me.

332
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:34,790
There was a price for my wish at that restaurant.

333
00:24:34,790 --> 00:24:37,360
Restaurant wish?

334
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:42,830
Hey, look at me. What did you say just now?

335
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:46,680
Witch's Diner.

336
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:52,720
Is it the place with a handsome student and a young owner?

337
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:55,150
Right, it is that place.

338
00:24:55,150 --> 00:24:58,260
 My wish was to get a job. I was desperate.

339
00:24:58,260 --> 00:25:01,800
 Are you Bae Yoon Gi?

340
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:05,490
 Nice to meet you. I am Bae Yoon Gi.

341
00:25:05,490 --> 00:25:07,910
 I'm finally meeting you.

342
00:25:07,910 --> 00:25:12,350
 You have no idea how much our Ga Young searched for you.

343
00:25:24,940 --> 00:25:29,320
 I also met Ga Young and got a job.

344
00:25:29,320 --> 00:25:33,490
I now believe in the miracle of that magic.

345
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:54,030
 That's right. What's there to do when you're dead but sleep as a rotting body?

346
00:25:54,030 --> 00:25:58,590
I'm so frustrated. I'm so frustrated.

347
00:26:01,020 --> 00:26:05,980
What did he say? "I can't marry someone whom I don't love."

348
00:26:05,980 --> 00:26:09,950
What's he doing now that he couldn't do when he was young? Huh?

349
00:26:09,950 --> 00:26:12,790
Now what can he do?

350
00:26:12,790 --> 00:26:17,240
He will only get it together if his mother dies.

351
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:20,390
So you have decided and come?

352
00:26:20,390 --> 00:26:21,720
Yes.

353
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:28,670
Didn't you say the food is very expensive here?

354
00:26:28,670 --> 00:26:33,040
Don't worry about money. I can just take something else in return.

355
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,520
Is that so?

356
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:39,560
What could an old woman like me give?

357
00:26:40,310 --> 00:26:47,670
All right. If my son can meet a match made in heaven and live a good life,

