372
00:27:58,510 --> 00:28:04,090
Don't carelessly judge someone else's happiness.

373
00:28:04,090 --> 00:28:08,850
Only they know whether it is happiness or misfortune.

374
00:28:08,850 --> 00:28:10,850
And,

375
00:28:12,010 --> 00:28:15,240
