376
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:18,130
Not for someone to become unhappy.

377
00:28:55,490 --> 00:28:58,380
Trust your instincts.

378
00:28:58,380 --> 00:29:01,110
You will definitely see it.

379
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:32,780
Noodles.

380
00:29:34,170 --> 00:29:37,260
It's janchi guksu (banquet noodles served at weddings and events).

381
00:30:48,070 --> 00:30:50,420
Grandmother, have this cup of tea.

