00:31:33,570 --> 00:31:35,780
Eat it, Grandmother.

384
00:31:35,780 --> 00:31:39,810
You have to desperately make your wish while eating it.

385
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:51,500
I don't know if I will ever

386
00:32:51,500 --> 00:32:56,630
be able to eat such delicious noodles again in my lifetime.

387
00:32:56,630 --> 00:33:00,830
Don't be silly, Grandma. You can just have it again at your son's wedding.

388
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:05,760
Yes, you're right about that.

389
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:12,410
Now that I made a wish, I can look forward to it, right?

