00:33:54,000 --> 00:33:56,040
A favor?

399
00:34:02,650 --> 00:34:05,610
- Hey, Noona. 
 - Huh?

400
00:34:05,610 --> 00:34:09,840
Oh, we're already here. You should go now, Gil Yong.

401
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:13,200
I live around here, too. It's been a few days since I moved in.

402
00:34:13,200 --> 00:34:14,700
That commercial building.

403
00:34:14,700 --> 00:34:17,070
Oh, I see.

404
00:34:17,070 --> 00:34:18,720
Yes.

405
00:34:21,220 --> 00:34:24,030
- By the way, Noona. 
 - Yes?

406
00:34:24,030 --> 00:34:29,040
I'm trying to buy a present for my father with my part-time job,

